{"tid":30451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好邪惡呀] 港女必食部隊鍋","createTime":"2016-12-09T07:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T06:10:10.000Z","uid":32832,"like":4,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d78e0d0cd144ad9db9ff84c9a72a9485776cade7","tid":30451,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6Ez2V9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6Ez2V9y.jpg&h=5b6efce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪糕店都有熱食唔係好出奇嘅，阿波羅一直都有賣燒賣、魚蛋、撈麵，不過最近趁天氣開始涼涼哋，推出全新嘅迷你韓國部隊鍋。Poster 寫晒韓文，唔知味道又夠唔夠韓呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7KBcrgK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7KBcrgK.jpg&h=ac5c3e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迷你部隊鍋 $28（加 $4 配芬達橙汁或提子汁）<br />\n所謂部隊鍋，原來唔係用鍋載嘅！可能係小食店關係，部隊鍋用紙碗載，方便捧住食。用辛辣麵，麵底即叫即煮。煮好麵條後，再倒入已放有辛辣麵調味粉嘅碗內加湯拌勻，再放午餐肉、泡菜、茄汁豆及芝士，細細碗嘅部隊鍋都幾多料喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lbea1KC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flbea1KC.jpg&h=06ecd209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迷你部隊鍋嘅精髓之一，梗係午餐肉啦！不過呢碗部隊鍋嘅午餐肉，有一塊係碎上。加上午餐肉無煎香過，吸引力大減！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EEZ1pjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEEZ1pjR.jpg&h=e133a7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有兩片車打芝士，放喺麵上受熱都有半融效果！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好邪惡呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cCrI9oQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcCrI9oQ.jpg&h=881b3b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n部隊鍋上面有 5、6 片泡菜，酸度剛好又唔太辣，質地爽脆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ro6qRoL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRo6qRoL.jpg&h=f8739104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n茄汁豆嘅分量就比較少，又無乜茄汁，拌勻都唔可以豐富部隊鍋湯底味道。提提想食嘅朋友，迷你部隊鍋唔係所有分店都有得賣，只有設熱食檔嘅分店先有㗎！"},{"pid":"efe82eb6f527363f9296072d52e1234eacb4f37b","tid":30451,"uid":32832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:50:55.000Z","msg":"韓狗屌你老母<br />\n呢d垃圾係得港女先食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隻狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"7c6a0fecff4a5596b826dadbdd64d58c971978f2","tid":30451,"uid":1517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c14d6fce61e974b914064664008f1445490342","tid":30451,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母又邊本垃圾雜誌呀！！！</span>"},{"pid":"d5d1e396c16652cc9d162b5d2966b63be258f1e7","tid":30451,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"狗飯"},{"pid":"2886b5d72c9f94e3a820e46342114e3d659b2503","tid":30451,"uid":35862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:53:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568a7e41df378db1440284c905befe90a89b887d","tid":30451,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾咪撚放出黎"},{"pid":"85dd784ab988ca5807d7dcc85d94b98f2db7346f","tid":30451,"uid":21963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"Apollo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099b7956fc9cb2e5f1a7816a13bc709660001f8a","tid":30451,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eab28310c04a82bd69db22618533ea591f25a89e","tid":30451,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"韓國妓女文化"},{"pid":"c320f9789d3975d8e3da16473660faff0d7ff097","tid":30451,"uid":60020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T